#!/bin/bash
#  ▄▄▄▄· • ▌ ▄ ·. ▪  ▄▄▌   ▄▄· .▄▄ ·   ──────────────────────
#  ▐█ ▀█▪·██ ▐███▪██ ██•  ▐█ ▌▪▐█ ▀.   ╔╦╗╔═╗╔╦╗╔═╗╦╦  ╔═╗╔═╗
#  ▐█▀▀█▄▐█ ▌▐▌▐█·▐█·██ ▪ ██ ▄▄▄▀▀▀█▄   ║║║ ║ ║ ╠╣ ║║  ║╣ ╚═╗
#  ██▄▪▐███ ██▌▐█▌▐█▌▐█▌ ▄▐███▌▐█▄▪▐█  ═╩╝╚═╝ ╩ ╚  ╩╩═╝╚═╝╚═╝
